These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, pepper
1. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Food   | avocado | pepper |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, horror
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
